name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Embedded input for BE-Search for D365 FO

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Access BE-terna Search from the navigation bar in Microsoft Dynamics 365 for Finance and Operations

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This browser extension places an input field for BE-Search in the navigation bar of all supporting cloud environments of Microsoft Dynamics 365 for Finance, Supply Chain Management & Commerce.

This browser extension only works in concert with BE-Search for Microsoft Dynamics 365 for Finance, Supply Chain Management & Commerce.
